            title: Seam 2 UI controls migration to JSF
          message: "Seam UI's `<s:link>` should be replaced by `<h:link>`.\n     \
            \                   There are differences in attributes, for example the\
            \ _action_ attribute maps to _outcome_ and there is no _propagation_ attribute."
